      <h1 class='title'>Probation Board for Northern Ireland: Business Plan 2004&#x2013;05</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='lords-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HL Deb 08 June 2004 vol 662 cc3-4WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_3ws' title='Col. 3WS &mdash; HL Deb 08 June 2004 vol 662 c3WS' name='column_3ws' href='#column_3ws' rel='bookmark'>3WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0662P0-06993'>
        <a name='S5LV0662P0_20040608_LWS_2'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-valerie-amos' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0662P0_20040608_LWS_2' title='Link to this speech by Ms Valerie Amos' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-valerie-amos" title="Ms Valerie Amos">Baroness Amos</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S5LV0662P0-06993">My right honourable friend the Secretary of State for Northern Ireland has made the following Ministerial Statement.</p><a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_4ws' title='Col. 4WS &mdash; HL Deb 08 June 2004 vol 662 c4WS' name='column_4ws' href='#column_4ws' rel='bookmark'>4WS</a><p id="S5LV0662P0-06994">I have today published the Probation Board for Northern Ireland's business plan for 2004&#x2013;05. The plan sets out the board's key objectives and performance targets for the year. Copies of the plan have today been placed in the libraries of both Houses.</p>
        </blockquote>
